reviewText: One of those things you loved when you were little and had to have it.  I remember having a VHS recording of this when it was on the Disney channel.  I recommend this movie for any family with a young boy

reviewText: When I bought this, I was expecting the real true movie... wrong. They took out a lot of the movie and edited a lot of stuff. I mean it's a good movie, but why cut parts out? Wasn't happy about that at all.

reviewText: I previously had the vhs tape of this movie so I was very happy to see it released on dvd.  The only thing I didn't care for were that some of the scenes were omitted, but the movie is still very funny and sends a positive message for all ages!!
